{"tid":1861270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國建議仍留在中國的美國人儲備糧食和其他用品(大撚鑊)","createTime":"2020-02-04T05:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T16:51:23.000Z","uid":125193,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"738e965df63f574395a77dc5a31e26e7d8c9ada4","tid":1861270,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:11:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506510-20200204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506510-20200204.htm&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=607c9a78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506510-20200204.htm&h=c989def8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506510-20200204.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3f857550ad7883f36f060fee4fd905e499e3a4ab","tid":1861270,"uid":125193,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"美國有5個州出現新型肺炎確診病例，總數11宗，其中加州有6宗，伊利諾伊州有2宗，華盛頓州、亞利桑那和馬薩諸塞州各有1宗。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發出通知，強烈呼籲仍然留在中國的美國公民，盡量留在家中，避免出席大型聚會及與其他人接觸，亦應考慮儲備糧食和其他用品，減少外出。通知又說，若果情況進一步惡化，美國使領館向仍留在中國的美國國民提供的協助可能會受到限制。<br />\n<br />\n國務卿蓬佩奧說，美國會再派包機，撤走在中國湖北省的美國公民。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院上星期已將對中國的旅遊警示，上調到最高級別，呼籲美國人不要前往中國旅遊。"},{"pid":"b2beb242b00410d74f0f038d3e78805988c56bfb","tid":1861270,"uid":275339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170019f9bc21f6c4f4d186ad8200095b5a50a012","tid":1861270,"uid":194824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:16:34.000Z","msg":"啲鬼佬用咩vpn"},{"pid":"b67d7dc818efda70246301a2abe96d498794a6bd","tid":1861270,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply